$ CSS properties: transition, transition-delay, transition-property, transition-timing-function

table { ll
  `transition-delay` ☰
  `transition-duration` ☰
  `transition-property` ☰
  `transition-timing-function` ☰
table }

`transition` is a *shorthand* to specify the values for all `transition-*` properties at once.

